{"tid":807571,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[Siri 的入境署工作手記] papers, please 直播！","createTime":"2018-09-05T15:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T07:22:29.000Z","uid":15867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bd53917d0d41d9b66e34f2b44126cdfb6a4664b9","tid":807571,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/225037_b706c5e3c1e5ef07631fbbd791b45079.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F225037_b706c5e3c1e5ef07631fbbd791b45079.png&h=5df0a01b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好以為點陣圖遊戲 冇靚畫面既遊戲就唔好玩唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時冇咩視覺效果 反而內容會好好</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/225254_c5bb93d74efaa03ac76663d094bf287f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F225254_c5bb93d74efaa03ac76663d094bf287f.png&h=b375f5e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲簡介：玩家扮演一位在虛構共產主義國家阿茲托卡（Arstotzka）中甫剛上任的邊界關卡檢查官，負責在每日早上六時至下午六時的開放時間審核、確認要入境人士的證件，遊戲的標題便是玩家面對每一位欲入境人士審查文件時的第一句台詞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://go.twitch.tv/sirihoihoi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.twitch.tv%2Fsirihoihoi&d=WCv99913tef268%2BYayrycHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=a7978e66\" target=\"_blank\">https://go.twitch.tv/sirihoihoi</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">台已開，歡迎大家入內吹水及討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">另外 黑色沙漠公會招人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/225623_46b6610fddece2c4922e052c92657024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F225623_46b6610fddece2c4922e052c92657024.png&h=bfcffb79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13ec86131992812ea2ebb671d9b89f06b10354c1","tid":807571,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de31764c3f00fbc340aafbc47b3f60302466dd12","tid":807571,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T16:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c90e9fc474db5f0ff95969b9225b7b89459c5e","tid":807571,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486f7bea49d7d625dead242790a1a15adbe863ca","tid":807571,"uid":43476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T16:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a464619c18167bbc4bec66b590f10464b1cf8d","tid":807571,"uid":141240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T16:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bd44e8863452f9f18f700de674393c396953a8","tid":807571,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T